I was a bit skeptical at first purchasing sunglasses from Amazon, didn't know if the price was worth it or if they would come looking completely different than the picture - but when these arrived in my mail I feel in love with them even more ! I'm super impressed with how UV protected they are, and having them polarized is an added bonus, especially when driving & on super sunny days ! Anti-reflective, UV protected and super cute to boot - 100% love these glasses and will definitely be looking to order more sunglasses from this company - they did not disappoint !
